            "title": "SkyDrive Becomes Japan’s First eVTOL Developer to Earn “Approved Design Organization” (ADO) Certification",
            "id": "3bf5acca-51b8-41a3-b327-6b882f1fee20",
            "description": "SkyDrive Inc., a prominent eVTOL aircraft manufacturer in Japan, has recently obtained the Approved Design Organization (ADO) certification from the Japan Civil Aviation Bureau, a branch of the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism. This significant achievement makes SkyDrive the inaugural dedicated eVTOL developer in Japan to be granted this esteemed certification. The ADO status is a crucial milestone that solidifies the company's position in the industry.",
